This is the README file for Bundle::CPANPLUS::Test::Reporter.

Please refer to 'perldoc Bundle::CPANPLUS::Test::Reporter' after 
installation for details.

#####################################################################

* Description

Bundle::CPANPLUS::Test::Reporter

    Bundle to install all modules required & desired by CPANPLUS to 
    provide automated test reporting to "testers.cpan.org"
    
#####################################################################

* Installation

Bundle::CPANPLUS::Test::Reporter follows the standard perl module 
install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

